Epoch 1:  Coherent 37/93 = 0.398   | Δ to ρ: 0.510
Epoch 10: Coherent 52/93 = 0.559   | Δ to ρ: 0.348
Epoch 20: Coherent 60/93 = 0.645   | Δ to ρ: 0.262
